, phonologically driven allomorph selection, subcategorization, optimization, distributed morphology, stratal optimality theory, word-and-paradigm morphology, morphology, phonology</td></tr><tr><td>previous versions: </td><td><a href="/lingbuzz/002774/v2.pdf?_s=9lYXebg81GP846Aw">v2 [January 2016]</a><br/><a href="/lingbuzz/002774/v1.pdf?_s=5YyJo6C5uV860_Jc">v1 [November 2015]</a><br/></td></tr>
